data.description: Don’t miss this amazing opportunity to own a home in a prime location with a stunning backyard. This three bed, two bath, two car garage home is located in a desirable and safe neighborhood, zoned for Hill Elementary, Bailey Jr High, & Arlington High. It offers a half acre yard with many beautiful trees, a generous covered patio, and a dazzling swimming pool. This is a rare and valuable chance to own a home with such a large yard and a pool in Arlington at this price. The home has several updates, including new flooring, new double pane insulated windows, and a new roof installed in August 2023. The kitchen has gas appliances and is open to the living room, giving it a cozy and friendly vibe. This home is ready for you to customize it to your liking. Schedule a showing today!
